                  </div>
                  <div class="medium-7 large-8 columns">
                    <p>Get the details and insight on our robust set of 24/7 towing services. Whether you're broke down at 3 PM, or 3 AM. We're the team you want to call.</p>
                    <p><a href="/services/24-hour-towing.html">READ MORE</a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>


              <hr>  


                <h3><a href="/services/flatbed-towing.html">Flatbed Towing</a></h3>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="medium-5 large-4 columns show-for-medium-up pr0">                  
                    <img src="/images/service_flatbed-towing.jpg" alt="Image of flatbed towing">
                  </div>
                  <div class="medium-7 large-8 columns">
                    <p>The safest way to transport your vehicle. Great for 4 wheel vehicles and other types of heavy machinery like excavators and other earth movers.</p>
                    <p><a href="/services/flatbed-towing.html">READ MORE</a></p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <hr>

